Sentencas: A series of W doped Pr0.5Ba0.5(Co0.7Fe0.3)O3-delta (PBCF) are prepared and characterized as cathodes for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cell (H-SOFC).
Titulo: High-performing proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells with triple-conducting cathode of Pr0.5Ba0.5(Co0.7Fe0.3)O3-δ tailored with W

Sentencas: The enhancement of proton migration and formation ability through W doping significantly increases the cell performance and it is further verified by the density functional theory (DFT) simulation, presenting the high valence element doping can be a potential approach for the design of cathode.
Titulo: High-performing proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells with triple-conducting cathode of Pr0.5Ba0.5(Co0.7Fe0.3)O3-δ tailored with W
